            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "Given the tight timeline we had to move through all phases of the project quickly. After a short discovery phase we focused our attention on content. The two lead UX designers got to work on a content map organizing content from the physical exhibition into pages, content pieces and navigation structures suited for digital consumption."
